Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.32,0:01:18.04,Main Dialogue (present),Saburou,0,0,0,,うるせえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.70,0:01:20.46,Main Dialogue Top (present),,0,0,0,,大丈夫ですか？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.58,0:01:25.70,Main Dialogue (present),Saburou,0,0,0,,んだよ もう｡
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.06,0:01:31.30,Main Dialogue (present),Saburou,0,0,0,,どこだよ？ 出口｡
