Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.78,0:06:05.33,Main Dialogue,,0,0,0,,あの うつけのような格好は｡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.33,0:06:06.70,Main Dialogue,,0,0,0,,早く ご挨拶を｡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.84,0:06:09.68,Main Dialogue,,0,0,0,,お父上の 信秀さまと 弟君の 信行さまです｡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.68,0:06:10.62,Main Dialogue (present),Saburou,0,0,0,,ＯＫ ＯＫ｡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.62,0:06:11.20,Main Dialogue,,0,0,0,,おっけえ？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.10,0:06:17.00,Main Dialogue (present),Saburou,0,0,0,,こんにちは｡
