Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.04,0:07:44.86,Main Dialogue (present),Saburou,0,0,0,,よーし｡ 者ども
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.28,0:07:46.72,Main Dialogue (present),Saburou,0,0,0,,かかれ｡
